Description.value: This integration flow issues an insurance policy in Policy Management in SAP S/4HANA by accepting a quotation created in SAP Quotation and Underwriting for Insurance. Additionally, the payment details are updated for the policyholder in SAP S/4HANA and for the premium payer in Policy Management in SAP S/4HANA.
